{"surah":102,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"102:1","arabic":" أَلْهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","id":"Bermegah-megahan telah melalaikan kamu,","words":[{"a":"أَلْهَىٰكُمُ","en":"Diverts you","id":"telah melalaikan kamu"},{"a":"ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","en":"the competition to increase","id":"berbanyak-banyak/bermegah-megah"}]},{"n":2,"key":"102:2","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ ٱلْمَقَابِرَ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"Until you visit the graveyards.","id":"sampai kamu masuk ke dalam kubur.","words":[{"a":"حَتَّىٰ","en":"Until","id":"hingga"},{"a":"زُرْتُمُ","en":"you visit","id":"kamu melewati/masuk"},{"a":"ٱلْمَقَابِرَ","en":"the graves","id":"kuburan-kuburan"}]},{"n":3,"key":"102:3","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"No! You are going to know.","id":"Sekali-kali tidak! Kelak kamu akan mengetahui (akibat perbuatanmu itu),","words":[{"a":"كَلَّا","en":"Nay","id":"sekali-kali tidak"},{"a":"سَوْفَ","en":"Soon","id":"kelak"},{"a":"تَعْلَمُونَ","en":"you will know","id":"(kalian) mengetahui"}]},{"n":4,"key":"102:4","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"Then, no! You are going to know.","id":"kemudian sekali-kali tidak! Kelak kamu akan mengetahui.","words":[{"a":"ثُمَّ","en":"Then","id":"kemudian"},{"a":"كَلَّا","en":"nay","id":"sekali-kali tidak"},{"a":"سَوْفَ","en":"Soon","id":"kelak"},{"a":"تَعْلَمُونَ","en":"you will know","id":"(kalian) mengetahui"}]},{"n":5,"key":"102:5","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوْ تَعْلَمُونَ عِلْمَ ٱلْيَقِينِ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty...","id":"Sekali-kali tidak! Sekiranya kamu mengetahui dengan pasti,","words":[{"a":"كَلَّا","en":"Nay","id":"sekali-kali tidak"},{"a":"لَوْ","en":"If","id":"jika"},{"a":"تَعْلَمُونَ","en":"you know","id":"(kalian) mengetahui"},{"a":"عِلْمَ","en":"(with) a knowledge","id":"pengetahuan"},{"a":"ٱلْيَقِينِ","en":"(of) certainty","id":"pasti/yakin"}]},{"n":6,"key":"102:6","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلْجَحِيمَ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"You will surely see the Hellfire.","id":"niscaya kamu benar-benar akan melihat neraka Jahim,","words":[{"a":"لَتَرَوُنَّ","en":"Surely you will see","id":"sungguh kamu akan melihat"},{"a":"ٱلْجَحِيمَ","en":"the Hellfire","id":"neraka Jahim"}]},{"n":7,"key":"102:7","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيْنَ ٱلْيَقِينِ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty.","id":"kemudian kamu benar-benar akan melihatnya dengan mata kepala sendiri,","words":[{"a":"ثُمَّ","en":"Then","id":"kemudian"},{"a":"لَتَرَوُنَّهَا","en":"surely you will see it","id":"sungguh kamu akan melihatnya"},{"a":"عَيْنَ","en":"(with the) eye","id":"mata/penglihatan"},{"a":"ٱلْيَقِينِ","en":"(of) certainty","id":"pasti/yakin"}]},{"n":8,"key":"102:8","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure.","id":"kemudian kamu benar-benar akan ditanya pada hari itu tentang kenikmatan (yang megah di dunia itu).","words":[{"a":"ثُمَّ","en":"Then","id":"kemudian"},{"a":"لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ","en":"surely you will be asked","id":"sungguh kamu akan ditanya"},{"a":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","en":"that Day","id":"pada hari itu"},{"a":"عَنِ","en":"about","id":"dari/tetang"},{"a":"ٱلنَّعِيمِ","en":"the pleasures","id":"kenikmatan"}]}]}